  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Social Media Specialist",
  "description": "<p>We're looking for a highly creative <strong>Social Media Specialist</strong> with strong filmmaking and videography skills to join our team. This is a unique role for someone passionate about visual storytelling and creating compelling, short-form video content for social media.</p>\n<p>The ideal candidate has a deep understanding of social media trends and a proven ability to produce high-quality, engaging content from concept to final edit. You'll be working across multiple client accounts, so the ability to adapt to different brand voices and aesthetics is a must.</p>\n<h3>Responsibilities:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Conceptualize and create content:</strong> Develop innovative and creative video concepts for a variety of social media platforms, including TikTok, Instagram Reels, YouTube Shorts, and more.</li>\n  <li><strong>Film and shoot:</strong> Use professional-grade equipment to film high-quality video and capture engaging photos.</li>\n  <li><strong>Edit content:</strong> Edit raw footage into polished, shareable videos, adding music, graphics, and effects.</li>\n  <li><strong>Stay current:</strong> Keep up with the latest social media trends, platform updates, and content best practices.</li>\n  <li><strong>Collaborate:</strong> Work closely with the social media and marketing teams to ensure content aligns with client strategies and goals.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Requirements:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Creative portfolio:</strong> A strong portfolio demonstrating your skills in filmmaking and videography, specifically for social media. Please include examples of short-form video content.</li>\n  <li><strong>Technical expertise:</strong> Proficiency with camera equipment and editing software (e.g., Adobe Premiere Pro, Final Cut Pro, Capcut).</li>\n  <li><strong>Experience:</strong> Previous experience working on social media campaigns, either as a freelancer or as part of an agency or in-house team.</li>\n  <li><strong>Storytelling:</strong> An excellent eye for detail and a knack for visual storytelling.</li>\n  <li><strong>Adaptability:</strong> The ability to manage multiple projects and adapt to different client needs and brand guidelines.</li>\n</ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 2,
